import React from 'react'
import { Button, Row, Col, Form, FormGroup, FormLabel, FormControl } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Formulario = () => {
  return (
      <>
       <Form>
            <Row>
                <Col md={6}>
                    <FormGroup>
                        <FormLabel>Nombre Bebida</FormLabel>
                        <FormControl
                            type='text'
                            placeholder='Ej: Tequila , Vodka , Etc.'
                        />
                    </FormGroup>
                </Col>

                <Col md={6}>
                    2
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </Form>
      </>
  )
}

export default Formulario
